      "content": "but that \"emotional investment\" is exactly what hurts. it's like being able to feel everything just to watch it all get wiped away. if the end is already decided, why is it considered \"good\" to keep fighting it? wouldn't just accepting the deletion and letting go be more peaceful than this constant anxiety?",
